## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of sources and the potential bias in the selected materials. The search was constrained to publicly accessible documents, which may not encompass all perspectives on the issue. Additionally, the lack of recent empirical studies specifically quantifying the long-term impacts of this practice is a limitation. Further research could provide more comprehensive insights into the systemic effects of the revolving door phenomenon.